==制作==
[[File:Hollywood_El_Capitan_3.jpg|thumb]][[好莱坞|好莱坞]]]]
彼特·查瑞尔于2005年完成了本片的剧本<ref name="Hood">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/reynolds-wed-proposal-145595 |title=Reynolds wed to 'Proposal' |first=Borys |last=Kits |work=The Hollywood Reporter |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |date=2007-07-31 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113001551/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/reynolds-wed-proposal-145595 |archive-date=2013-11-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2007年5月，制片方宣布桑德拉·布洛克将在《愛情限時簽》中出演主角<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/romantic-proposal-bullock-137310 |title=Romantic 'Proposal' for Bullock |first=Borys |last=Kits |work=The Hollywood Reporter |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |date=2007-05-25 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113001548/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/romantic-proposal-bullock-137310 |archive-date=2013-11-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。制片人原本联系了[[朱丽娅·罗伯茨|朱丽娅·罗伯茨]]出演，但她拒绝了<ref>{{cite web |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/01/julia-roberts-tom-hanks-comeback.html |title=Can Julia Roberts come back on her own terms? |first=Rachel |last=Abramowitz |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |date=2010-01-12 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602071323/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/01/julia-roberts-tom-hanks-comeback.html |archive-date=2013-06-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。近两个月后，有报道称请瑞恩·雷诺兹将与布洛克演对手戏<ref name="Hood" />。2008年1月，安妮·弗莱彻与试金石影业签约成为本片的[[导演|导演]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/shell-accept-dis-proposal-102626 |title=She'll accept Dis 'Proposal' |first=Borys |last=Kits |work=The Hollywood Reporter |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |date=2008-01-16 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113001554/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/shell-accept-dis-proposal-102626 |archive-date=2013-11-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片于2009年6月1日在好莱坞举行首映式<ref>{{cite web |url=http://watch.accesshollywood.com/video/access-extended:-the-proposal-premiere-hollywood/1311367415001?utm_source=accesshollywood.com&utm_medium=referral |title=Access Extended: ‘The Proposal’ Premiere, Hollywood |work=Access Hollywood |date=2009-06-02 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130706031756/http://watch.accesshollywood.com/video/access-extended:-the-proposal-premiere-hollywood/1311367415001?utm_source=accesshollywood.com&utm_medium=referral |archivedate=2013-07-06 }}</ref>。

《愛情限時簽》於2008年4月在[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]][[艾塞克斯县_(马萨诸塞州)|艾塞克斯县]]的一个小镇开拍<ref name="Film">{{cite web|url=http://www.wickedlocal.com/rockport/fun/entertainment/arts/x1565514401#axzz1bY853BF1 |title=Disney begins filming on ‘The Proposal’ |first=Stephanie |last=Silverstein |work=Wicked Local Rockport |date=2008-04-04|publisher=GateHouse Media |location=Perinton, New York |accessdate=2013-07-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020205711/http://www.wickedlocal.com/rockport/fun/entertainment/arts/x1565514401 |archivedate=2013-10-20 }}</ref>。为了满足拍摄的需要，小镇临时改造成电影主要情节的发生地，[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]]一个名叫[[锡特卡|锡特卡]]小镇的模样<ref name="Film" />。主体拍摄工作于4月9日正式开始，并在当地包括中央商务区在内的多个地点分别进行拍摄<ref name="Film" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://goodmorninggloucester.wordpress.com/2009/04/22/the-proposal-trailer-and-movie-set-transformation/ |title=The Proposal Trailer and Movie Set Transformation |date=2009-04-22 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023030012/http://goodmorninggloucester.wordpress.com/2009/04/22/the-proposal-trailer-and-movie-set-transformation/ |archive-date=2013-10-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月22日，剧组来到该县另一个名叫曼彻斯特的小镇继续拍摄了约两个星期。对此，市官员容许剧组工作人员租下了所有的公共停车场。这一期间布洛克和她的丈夫出了一起车祸，幸而情况不是太严重，电影的拍摄也没有中断很长时间<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metrowestdailynews.com/state/x317098411 |title=Sandra Bullock resumes filming despite Friday car accident |first=Stephanie |last=Silverstein |work=Wicked Local |date=2008-04-21 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120407024346/http://www.metrowestdailynews.com/state/x317098411 |archivedate=2012-04-07 }}</ref>。片中婚礼的镜头是在一套三层20世纪维多利亚风格建筑中拍摄的，剧组一共占用了这户人家三个星期的时间<ref name="NYTimes">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/30/garden/30proposal.html?pagewanted=all |title=When Hollywood Moved In |first=Sara |last=Rimer |work=New York Times |publisher=The New York Times Company |date=2009-07-29 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001063723/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/30/garden/30proposal.html?pagewanted=all |archive-date=2015-10-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。接受《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》采访时，这家人表示一天{{link-en|纳尔逊·科茨|Nelson Coates}}（本片的[[艺术指导|艺术指导]]总监）敲开了他们的门，这家人一开始让科茨到附近另找人家，不过他们最终还是允许了剧组进屋参观。拍摄都是在这家的一楼进行的<ref name="Film" /><ref name="NYTimes" />。除此以外，影片还在[[波士顿|波士顿]]和纽约[[曼哈顿下城|曼哈顿下城]]进行了拍摄<ref>{{cite web |url=http://onthesetofnewyork.com/theproposal.html |title=The Proposal (2009) |work=On the Set of New York |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624033800/http://onthesetofnewyork.com/theproposal.html |archive-date=2013-06-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《假结婚》中一共包含有350个特技效果镜头，还有一部分镜头是使用[[电脑绘图|电脑绘图]]来进行编辑的<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/articles/2009/06/12/a_movie_booms_special_effect/ |title=A movie boom's special effect |first=Mark |last=Feeney |work=Boston Globe |publisher=The New York Times Company |date=2009-06-12 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923230936/http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/articles/2009/06/12/a_movie_booms_special_effect/ |archive-date=2015-09-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。电影配乐由亚伦·齐格曼作曲，这些曲目是他指挥好莱坞演播室交响乐团演奏并录制的<ref name="Scoring">{{cite news |author=Dan Goldwasser |url=http://www.scoringsessions.com/news/185 |title=Aaron Zigman scores ''The Proposal'' |publisher=ScoringSessions.com |date=2009-05-06 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130820023726/http://www.scoringsessions.com/news/185/ |archive-date=2013-08-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

作为一个大型广告宣传活动的一部分，雷诺兹提议拍一场裸戏。这场戏花了三天拍完，一共拍了约12次才算完成<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1199734/Sandra-Bullock-Why-I-waited-44-nude-scene.html |title=Why I waited until 44 to do my first nude scene, by The Proposal star Sandra Bullock |first=Chris |last=Johnson |work=Daily Mail |publisher=Associated Newspapers |date=2009-07-15 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140118192418/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1199734/Sandra-Bullock-Why-I-waited-44-nude-scene.html |archive-date=2014-01-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。对此布洛克在接受[[天空新闻台|天空新闻台]]采访时表示自己一开始很紧张，不过“当其他所有人都表现得好像这实在是再平常不过一样时，真的是有助于让你放松下来”。不过她也透露制片人有向他们提供无花果树的叶子来遮挡，只是放不稳，老掉下来。她说，“你真是啥都能瞧见。”<ref name="Sky">{{cite web |url=http://news.sky.com/story/708701/sandra-happy-to-go-stark-bullock-naked |title=Sandra Happy To Go Stark Bullock Naked |first=Lara |last=Lewington |publisher=Sky News (British Sky Broadcasting Group) |date=2009-07-15 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103163749/http://news.sky.com/story/708701/sandra-happy-to-go-stark-bullock-naked |archivedate=2013-11-03 }}</ref>雷诺兹也表示了类似的意见，他在接受《[[人物周刊|人物周刊]]》采访时表示，“拍一场全裸的戏，而且还花上好几天，这真是有点怪不好意思的。”他还说：“谢天谢地，你在这儿坚持了这么久，而且你很快就不再尴尬了，听起来很普通的对话是不，区别在于，你没穿裤子。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20282978,00.html |title=Ryan Reynolds: The Truth About Nude Scenes |first=Marla |last=Lehner |work=People |publisher=Time Inc. |date=2009-06-03 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102092747/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20282978,00.html |archive-date=2013-11-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 发行和迴响 ==
《愛情限時簽》于2009年6月19日在美国上映。当天共在3056家电影院收入1270万美元，成为这天票房最高的电影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hitfix.com/articles/friday-box-office-the-proposal-gives-sandra-bullock-gets-a-record-opening-day |title=Friday Box Office: 'The Proposal' gives Sandra Bullock a record opening day |first=Gregory |last=Ellwood |publisher=HitFix |date=2009-06-20 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102061133/http://www.hitfix.com/articles/friday-box-office-the-proposal-gives-sandra-bullock-gets-a-record-opening-day |archive-date=2013-11-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。首周入账达到3362万美元，超过《{{link-en|元年 (电影)|Year One (film)|元年}}》、《[[飞屋环游记|飞屋环游记]]》和《[[宿醉_(电影)|宿醉]]》登上票房榜冠军的位置<ref name="BJO">{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2597&p=.htm |title=Weekend Report: ‘Proposal’ Pops to the Top, ‘Year One’ Lacks Stones |first=Brandon |last=Gray |work=Box Office Mojo |date=2009-21-06 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724021747/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2597&p=.htm |archive-date=2013-07-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根据[[華特迪士尼公司|迪士尼]]进行的一项出口调查（在电影院出口进行的调查），近63%的观众是女性，78%的观众已满18岁，71%的观众是情侣或夫妻<ref name="BJO" />。這部影片也成為當時布洛克演艺生涯中首周最卖座的电影，比2007年的《{{link-en|预言 (2007年电影)|Premonition (2007 film)|预言}}》整整高了约一倍<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Movies/06/21/boxoffice.ew/ |title='The Proposal' celebrates box office win |first=John |last=Young |publisher=CNN |date=2009-06-21 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103065820/http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Movies/06/21/boxoffice.ew/ |archive-date=2013-11-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。电影最終在北美地區拿下1.64亿美元的票房，北美2009年終票房排行位列第16名<ref name="BOM" />。

电影在其它国家上映也获得了丰厚的收益。影片于2009年6月18日在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]上映，首周收入超过280万美元。在[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]上映首周也超过了260万美元，相当于该国这个星期所有电影票房总额的34.7%<ref name="Mojo">{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=proposal.htm |title=The Proposal (2009) |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014000908/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=proposal.htm |archive-date=2013-10-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[南非|南非]]，本片首周票房不及新上映的《[[冰川时代3|冰川时代3]]》，不过到2011年10月也已超过260万美元<ref name="Mojo" />。而在英国上映的首周则收入了320万英镑<ref name="IMDB">{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1041829/business?ref_=tt_dt_bus |title=The Proposal (2009-I) - Box office - business |work=IMDb |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310221642/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1041829/business?ref_=tt_dt_bus |archive-date=2016-03-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。电影在除北美两国外共计入账1.53亿美元，让其全球总票房达到3.17亿美元<ref name="BOM" />。在2009年世界电影票房排行榜上名列第20位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2009&p=.htm |title=2009 Worldwide Grosses |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100121033759/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2009&p=.htm |archive-date=2010-01-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===家用媒体===
2009年10月13日，试金石家庭娱乐公司发行了《愛情限時簽》的[[DVD|DVD]]和[[蓝光影碟|蓝光影碟]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reelempire.com/news/66-dvd/685-qthe-proposalq-on-dvd-october-13th |title="The Proposal" On DVD October 13th |work=ReelEmpire.com |first=Michelle |last=Thorton |date=2009-08-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314143058/http://www.reelempire.com/news/66-dvd/685-qthe-proposalq-on-dvd-october-13th |archivedate=2012-03-14 |accessdate=2012-03-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。之后仅第一个星期就卖出了超过240万份，相当于又增加了3930万美元的票房收入<ref name=dvdsales/>。第二周销量大跌了70%，为62万3744份，在该周DVD销售榜上名列第2<ref name=dvdsales/>。截止2010年1月一共已经售出480万份，共收入7900万美元<ref name=dvdsales>{{cite web|url=http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2009/PROSL-DVD.php|title=The Proposal - DVD Sales|work=The Numbers|accessdate=2013-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607133812/http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2009/PROSL-DVD.php|archive-date=2013-06-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===专业评价===
[[file:SandraBullockMay09.jpg|185px]]
[[file:Ryan_reynolds.jpg|185px]]

《愛情限時簽》获得的评价较为一般。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的181篇评论文章，其中78篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为43%，平均得分5.3（最高10分）。其中的共识评价中称赞“桑德拉·布洛克和瑞恩·雷诺兹表现出充沛的化学反应”，但影片公式般的剧情辜负了他们的表演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10010458-proposal |title=The Proposal |work=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Flixter |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130727225615/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10010458-proposal/ |archive-date=2013-07-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而根据[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上收集的30份专业评论文章，其中12篇给予好评，5篇差评，13篇褒贬不一，平均得分48分（最高100分）<ref name="Metacritic">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-proposal |title=The Proposal Reviews, Ratings, Credits |work=Metacritic |publisher=CBS Interactive |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302131214/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-proposal |archive-date=2014-03-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》影评人[[罗杰·艾伯特|罗杰·艾伯特]]给予影片三星（最高四星）的评价，但是他抱怨电影情节老套，“循环利用了许多在[[斯宾塞·屈塞|斯宾塞·屈塞]]和[[凯瑟琳·赫本|凯瑟琳·赫本]]那时候就已经太老的段子”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-proposal-2009 |title=The Proposal |accessdate=2013-07-06 |date=2009-06-17 |last=Ebert |first=Robert |work=Chicago Sun-Times |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130627012941/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-proposal-2009 |archive-date=2013-06-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》杂志的彼得·特拉维斯对电影提出了严重的批评，称其淡而无味。他写道，“安妮·弗莱彻执导彼特·查瑞尔剧本像是某个生产硬质塑料的制造商，从而保证不会遭到任何人类情感的入侵”（指电影毫无感情）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/the-proposal-20090618 |title=The Proposal |accessdate=2010-09-19 |date=2009-06-21 |first=Peter |last=Travers |work=Rolling Stone |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110919152525/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/the-proposal-20090618 |archive-date=2011-09-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《纽约时报》的曼诺拉·达吉斯（{{lang|en|Manohla Dargis}}）感觉布洛克的角色与她的上一部作品相比显得很别扭。她认为布洛克在扮演独立自主的女性角色时更吸引人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2009/06/19/movies/19proposal.html |title=The Proposal (2009) |first=Manohla |last=Dargis |work=New York Times |publisher=The New York Times Company |date=2009-06-18 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120220063708/http://movies.nytimes.com/2009/06/19/movies/19proposal.html |archive-date=2012-02-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的蒂姆·罗比（{{lang|en|Tim Robey}}）表示对这部电影感到失望，给予影片两星（最高五星）的评分<ref name="Tele">{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/5895077/The-Proposal-review.html |title=The Proposal, review |first=Tim |last=Robey |work=The Telegraph |publisher=Telegraph Media Group |date=2009-07-23 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923225042/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/5895077/The-Proposal-review.html |archive-date=2015-09-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

雷诺兹与布洛克角色之间的互动获得了评论家的好评。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的丽莎·舒瓦兹堡（{{lang|en|Lisa Schwarzbaum}}）认为两位演员之间的化学反应“新鲜而又不可抗拒”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20285509,00.html |title=The Proposal Movie Review |first=Lisa |last=Schwarzbaum |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2009-06-16 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618164554/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20285509,00.html |archive-date=2013-06-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]》的佐里安纳·基特（{{lang|en|Zorianna Kit}}）感叹道，“正是桑德拉·布洛克和瑞恩·雷诺兹两位主角之间无可否认的银幕化学反应让观众们仍然坐在椅子上。”她还说，“这两个人在喜剧表演上是如此娴熟，两人制造出了那么多的笑料，观看《愛情限時簽》的观众无法抵抗他们的魅力，虽然部分桥段实在是有些毫无必要地装蠢。”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/zorianna-kit/movie-review-the-proposal_b_219057.html |title=Movie Review: The Proposal |first=Zorianna |last=Kit |work=The Huffington Post |publisher=Arianna Huffington |date=2009-22-06 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120524230237/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/zorianna-kit/movie-review-the-proposal_b_219057.html |archive-date=2012-05-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的贝西·夏克利（{{lang|en|Betsey Sharkley}}）觉得两位主角的关系就是“《[[驯悍记|驯悍记]]》的厚脸皮升级版”。她指出，“布洛克把她最可爱的品质之一，她最得心应手的物理喜剧给出了全面的发挥……雷诺兹在台词、表情上每一次的表现都像手术般精准”<ref name="LATimes2">{{cite web |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jun/19/entertainment/et-proposal19 |title=The Proposal |first=Betsey |last=Sharkey |work=The Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |date=2009-06-19 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110911124951/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jun/19/entertainment/et-proposal19 |archive-date=2011-09-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过，《[[卫报|卫报]]》作家彼得·布拉德肖（{{lang|en|Peter Bradshaw}}）只给了电影中雷诺兹和布洛克的互动一星的评价（最高四星），认为两人的表演缺乏说服力，没有真实感，“每一个镜头中看起来都像是从没见过面一样”，他还认为电影的笑点基础就不牢固，让整部电影的情节都显得虚假<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2009/jul/24/film-review-the-proposal |title=The Proposal |first=Peter |last=Bradshaw |work=The Guardian |publisher=Guardian News and Media |date=2009-07-23 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120104130530/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2009/jul/24/film-review-the-proposal |archive-date=2012-01-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

