==重拍==
2012年上映的[[马拉雅拉姆语|马拉雅拉姆语]][[印度|印度]]电影《我的老板》（{{lang|en|My Boss}}）是《愛情限時簽》的一部重拍片，影片在[[孟买|孟买]]和[[喀拉拉邦|喀拉拉邦]]取景<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sify.com/movies/Mamta-to-play-Dileep-s-boss-imagegallery-malayalam-mfjpdIhfaed.html?html=5 |title=Mamta to play Dileep's boss |work=Sify |date=2012-04-23 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120620174242/http://www.sify.com/movies/Mamta-to-play-Dileep-s-boss-imagegallery-malayalam-mfjpdIhfaed.html?html=5 |archive-date=2012-06-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Shruti Karthikeyan |date=2012-04-23 |url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/channels/showbiz/mollywood/dileep-mamta-my-boss-939 |title=Dileep, Mamta in My Boss |publisher=''Deccan Chronicle'' |location=Madras |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120604221030/http://www.deccanchronicle.com/channels/showbiz/mollywood/dileep-mamta-my-boss-939 |archivedate=2012-06-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。该片基本的故事情节与《愛情限時簽》相同，不过还是包含有许多不同的元素<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/slide-show/slide-show-1-south-theater-strike-called-off-in-kerala/20121109.htm|title=Theater strike called off in Kerala|publisher=Rediff|date=2011-11-09|accessdate=2013-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230232203/http://www.rediff.com/movies/slide-show/slide-show-1-south-theater-strike-called-off-in-kerala/20121109.htm|archive-date=2013-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两位主角分别由迪利普（{{lang|en|Dileep}}，音译）和曼塔·莫汉达斯（{{lang|en|Mamta Mohandas}}，音译）扮演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiaglitz.com/channels/malayalam/article/71821.html|title=Dileep, Mamtha again for 'My Boss'|publisher=IndiaGlitz|date=2011-10-08|accessdate=2013-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212101203/http://www.indiaglitz.com/channels/malayalam/article/71821.html|archive-date=2013-12-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这部重拍片在商业上也很成功<ref>{{cite web |author=Paresh C Palicha |date=2012-11-12 |url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/south-review-my-boss-is-a-loud-copy-of-a-hollywood-film/20121112.htm |title=Review: My Boss is a loud copy of a Hollywood film |work=Rediff.com |accessdate=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130915063713/http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/south-review-my-boss-is-a-loud-copy-of-a-hollywood-film/20121112.htm |archive-date=2013-09-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

